To configure a new system, run in the following order (mainly tested on OS X):

Prerequisites
=============

* Set up your SSH keys

Installation
============

* brew_updates.sh   --- install homebrew packages (OS X only)
* pip_install.sh    --- install python packages
* ruby.sh           --- install ruby dependencies and gems
* npm.sh            --- install npm packages
* setup_env.sh      --- do final setup (vim configuration, etc.)

